# Ignore everything by default
/*

# Whitelist custom tools and containers
!/scripts/
!/containers/

# --- PRIVACY & SECRETS ---
# Ignore the Caddyfile and all secret environment files
**/caddy/Caddyfile
*.env

# --- CONTAINER DATA (Ignore heavy/dynamic files) ---

# Caddy
**/caddy_data/
**/caddy_config/

# Uptime Kuma
**/uptime-kuma/data/

# Crafty (Ignore all server files, backups, and the database)
**/crafty/import/
**/crafty/backups/
**/crafty/logs/
**/crafty/servers/
**/crafty/docker/

# Syncthing (Ignore the actual synced data and internal database)
**/containers/syncthing/data/
**/containers/syncthing/config/

# --- GENERAL CLUTTER ---
**/*.log
**/*.db
**/*.sqlite
.DS_Store
